Invocation Name: home maintenance tips
des:
Ask Alexa for an interesting list of facts about home maintenance and simple repair tips. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next fact. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
This skill was created by Power Properties Ltd., a full service property management company located in Calgary, Alberta.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
